Description:

Chrome Search Engines resources, including, but not limited to:

- Set of prepopulated engines,
- Country associations,
- Translations,
- Images,
etc.

The contents of this repository are populated by an automated process.
Do not modify the content directly.

For search provider data, please see:
- the schema for engines definitions, which gives more info on the supported
  fields and possible values: `prepopulated_engines_schema.json`
- https://crbug.com/new?component=1710335&template=2222632 which is the bug
  template to propose any changes (additions, updates, or removals). Chrome
  engineers will review, verify, and apply the proposed changes.
